Package: mlcenter
Title: Centering in Multilevel Data
Version: 1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Dominik", "Vollbracht", , "d.vollbracht@rptu.de", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: This ligthweight package contains functions for centering multilevel data. This applies to group mean centering at level 1 (or person mean centering if data points are nested in persons) and grand mean centering at level 2.
License: use_mit_license()
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.2
Depends: 
    R (>= 3.5)
LazyData: true
